rrectly is important for organization.\\n\\n**Considering class metadata requirements**\\n\\nI'm pondering if the argument string from `Class.getName().replace` should be a constant. Inside the library, it’s more dynamic, and I wonder if the native image might include test classes since they can be referenced with class literals in constants. Using class literals can help with naming and assertions, making classes reachable. Even without metadata, `Class.forName` may still require reflection metadata for a native image. Tracking this seems essential.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_07083aa4e0d3106d0169ef6f6ad8008196aa2f9b91b81a91eb\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp7297_41gsQ6s2a3b7CuC8J0V3_00BQ0VfPLK6ft_Lr3TzRAbnJiDTIDsfMxc7wZSBmqG7YPMlPoDRcC2gwXcW2_DdjGDEB4ojuB2qtWK2z8PhACJ0vHwpZ8LMmgEDWIB7KbLtlGb83QodRPffTXAEZXDss9VEv1c5GHyhODA-hAo_WTJia9pG9TtClH_5w8dZJK6arAhxiF5NlND6Fg9BDFEgvD36j3zZzLzeigv3pJxI3eaxRShI6pih9gXoFjPDX0wtAE4APuRKQWKFW2uyNzBCMQU-wzGHTjfdYZtZwy0cUXgPP7LGWgaSTs9CjUO6UUliv66rWsGsAqhXsICegm6qOuhtPP-ZyrL-naZyBnKpUiYBFdKtwC_bfpeAVEXtxx7SdRjNeMQYnt6YqFMYueJ5bE5Jx7Yd0tsy9vYMH7JuofOvZW4ZCh-EI9KsWXsmTG38e_Aw_UtKVh1rvGDN2sW-Fti4rPCq6jhaW-IprE9_zejGgaeLJrP02BU9xQroSutSn-TJuaIKfHciRTczIk5W39tE-3LEvEe1h1LBziTltwKz-39mnXdTJwrUZpj3uhl7EVvJQ4gUCpnjsctRNAY_z0BO9EdjuFKrpw8Z4SiRX_AqplYqEVuFzP0QCTvnP7MjKw0rZgbIlrAgoD6MA6Zw6_DT85J7zGGWuw2Q4yOHbAmQ_q7lBgbNi4jtckUVHzCbJz4BuXw1ZFyfiI8wOfM0g_NhvSDqZce7B98iciX17gFKjyv6aCsnD178Uv7JE5gUFPMn2AUi9DVI-ArOrsiVlzAw2Fk3V2jLdaYSN9B0oXetmtoGndvNXPL4-mlDjkHA2KG-ERO2_yB127uv-DWL-e-JRDpPrzawiUUX-J4QsCUPCnt6RmqcAKOAgpOq8fhAvbQOy-AaQ6CV7JQcjFffQjO1n3QItOYjI7TcQB3nn8obmTr6msbnqnytGAZIee1Ytv6AC38_FYV56tePkr_2oobz_Jfo1ZH8wQ3pkXZVlF6KYKUM-QsATd62GZDXSeSa2Ruh1eBn-BvpRJBiTOid5xLxG14dmwsDbkWOZtThR2MIfwSKDNGZHuuTkuVd5HtzRFY1THZeyq_uQ4DUgAfkuZHu6I7LeaPmW2FdNAETjyXyx3_3hbcgRkGjKrCdSVrKFAXAkBWXtjYKz7l9yoc6N8TY46dV4pWdx32NGyOojCmo3PkOVqEXrtMp-SvOQtHpYWbL_TkOWA11Xy7d_gA4GMuJVpiYEbny0ynM2AwN5f5vDi5MXb5